# JFrog Platform Conventions

- Always create and manage policies within a JFrog Project unless the user explicitly opts out.
- templates, rules  and policies name format: 2-32 lowercase alphanumeric characters, must start with a letter.
- templates, rules  and policies description format: 2-100 alphanumeric characters, must start with a letter.
- Prefer using existing templates, rules and policies
- Create policies in this order: template, rules, then policy.

